WEBVTT

00:01.968 --> 00:05.405
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:05.405 --> 00:09.492
I know, Dad, but still...

00:09.492 --> 00:11.795
Well, whatever you think is best, Dad.

00:11.795 --> 00:13.296
Right.

00:13.296 --> 00:16.299
Bye, Dad.

00:16.299 --> 00:17.167
That was my dad.

00:17.167 --> 00:18.918
Really.

00:18.918 --> 00:22.305
Yeah, he's threatening to make
me move back home to Indiana.

00:22.305 --> 00:24.174
He's been talking to my Uncle Fergie.

00:24.174 --> 00:25.642
The guy who was here last week?

00:25.642 --> 00:27.010
I thought he had a great time.

00:27.010 --> 00:28.261
Well, he did.

00:28.261 --> 00:31.264
But all he told them about was
the two times he got mugged.

00:31.264 --> 00:33.099
Oh, that was just bad luck. Yeah.

00:33.099 --> 00:34.067
Woody, you've lived here two years.

00:34.067 --> 00:35.068
How many times you been mugged?

00:35.068 --> 00:36.352
Ten. But...

00:37.737 --> 00:40.023
You know, that's including the
two times with Uncle Fergie.

00:40.023 --> 00:41.574
Oh.

00:41.574 --> 00:44.911
So now my parents are convinced
that Boston is a dangerous town

00:44.911 --> 00:47.163
and all my friends are seedy lowlifes.

00:47.163 --> 00:49.499
Well, surely they don't want
you to go back to Indiana

00:49.499 --> 00:50.867
because we're a corrupting influence.

00:50.867 --> 00:51.618
Well, who knows?

00:51.618 --> 00:54.621
Somehow, they got the idea
that every guy in Boston

00:54.621 --> 00:56.506
is some lonely, pathetic weirdo.

00:56.506 --> 00:58.458
Look, is this or is this not

00:58.458 --> 00:59.959
the spitting image of George Schultz?

01:02.846 --> 01:05.131
So, uh, Woody, what
time does your bus leave?

01:07.550 --> 01:11.471
(piano plays)

01:11.471 --> 01:13.940
? Making your way in the world today ?

01:13.940 --> 01:16.943
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:16.943 --> 01:19.946
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:19.946 --> 01:22.949
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:22.949 --> 01:28.204
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:28.204 --> 01:30.990
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:30.990 --> 01:35.995
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:35.995 --> 01:41.000
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:41.000 --> 01:43.002
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:43.002 --> 01:46.005
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:46.005 --> 01:51.010
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

01:51.010 --> 01:54.013
? You want to go where people know ?

01:54.013 --> 01:56.015
? People are all the same ?

01:56.015 --> 02:01.020
? You want to go where
everybody knows your name. ?

